Package: LGrafEU
Type: Package
Title: Agricultural landscape generator
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Eyal Goldstein, Antonia Deutcher, Eamon O'keeffe, Sebastian Hanss 
Maintainer: Eyal Goldstein <pogoyoly@gmail.com>
Description: Generates artificial agricultural landscapes 
    <link to publicationn>
    Artificial agricultural landscape generators are designed to 
    systematically and realistically produce artificial maps of 
    agricutltural dominated landscapes, which are meant to be used 
    as an input for ecological models. 
    
